$ Oracle: online statistics gathering

For certain operations, Oracle gathers → development/databases/Oracle/optimizer/statistics automatically, that is, without having to explicitely call
→ development/databases/Oracle/installed/packages/dbms/stats[`dbms_stats`]:
  • Creation of an → development/databases/Oracle/objects/indexes[index]
  • Create table as select (CTAS)
  • Insert as select (IAS) into empty → development/databases/Oracle/objects/tables[tables]

links:
  As so often, Dani Schnider → https://danischnider.wordpress.com/2015/12/23/online-statistics-gathering-in-oracle-12c/[covers the subject in his blog].
